Description: This is an awesome guitar and it comes with its own custom gig-bag/backpack with the show and Cartoon Network logo on it.The guitar is in GREAT shape except for a few nicks which are all on the rear or rear-bottom (see photos). The front is is near-mint or mint shape.These guitars are super hard to find these days and this appears to be the only one to appear on eBay in quite awhile. HERE'S THE ORIGINAL PRESS RELEASE FROM 2002:Coinciding with this summer's release of the PowerPuff Girls movie, DaisyRock has designed and manufactured two styles of electric guitars for Cartoon Network.The PowerPuff Girls guitar is based on Daisy Rock's Heartbreaker model. This heart-shaped electric is adorned with Blossom, Bubbles and Buttercup and is finished in an eye-catching 3-Tone Pink! The guitar features a 22 1/2" scale neck and a single, full-range humbucking pickup.Both guitars have pearloid 'star' inlays and include a cool combination padded gig bag / back pack.Like all Daisy Rock guitars and basses, these two guitars are designed with a slim neck shape and profile, which is perfect for smaller hands.
Title: VERY RARE and COLLECTIBLE Powerpuff Girls! Electric Guitar (2002)
